quran[18]{c,v,t,f}:
  37,127,"Wọ́n sì pè é ní òpùrọ́. Nítorí náà, wọ́n máa mú wọn wá sínú Iná."
  37,128,"Àfi àwọn ẹrúsìn Allāhu, àwọn tí A ṣà lẹ́ṣà (fún ìgbàgbọ́ òdodo)."
  37,129,"A fún un ní orúkọ rere láààrin àwọn ẹni ìkẹ́yìn."
  40,70,"Àwọn tó pe Tírà náà àti ohun tí A fi rán àwọn Òjíṣẹ́ Wa níṣẹ́ ní irọ́, láìpẹ́ wọ́n máa mọ̀."
  40,71,"Nígbà tí àwọn sẹ́kẹ́sẹkẹ̀ àti ẹ̀wọ̀n bá wà ní ọrùn wọn, tí wọn yóò fi máa wọ́ wọn"
  40,72,"sínú omi tó gbóná parí. Lẹ́yìn náà, wọn yóò fi wọ́n ko Iná."
  41,49,"Ènìyàn kò kó ṣúṣú níbi àdúà (láti tọrọ) oore. Tí aburú bá sì fọwọ́ bà á, ó máa di olùsọ̀rètínù, olùjákànmùná."
  41,50,"Dájúdájú tí A bá ṣe ìdẹ̀ra fún un láti ọ̀dọ̀ Wa lẹ́yìn aburú tí ó fọwọ́ bà á, dájúdájú ó máa wí pé: “Èyí ni tèmi. Èmi kò sì ní àmọ̀dájú pé Àkókò náà máa ṣẹlẹ̀. Àti pé dájúdájú tí Wọ́n bá dá mi padà sí ọ̀dọ̀ Olúwa mi, dájúdájú rere tún wà fún mi ní ọ̀dọ̀ Rẹ̀.” Dájúdájú Àwa yóò fún àwọn tó ṣàì gbàgbọ́ ní ìró ohun tí wọ́n ṣe níṣẹ́. Dájúdájú A sì máa fún wọn ní ìyà tó nípọn tọ́ wò."
  41,51,"Àti pé nígbà tí A bá ṣe ìdẹ̀ra fún ènìyàn, ó máa gbúnrí (kúrò ní ọ̀dọ̀ Wa). Ó sì máa ṣègbéraga. Nígbà tí aburú bá sì fọwọ́ bà á, nígbà náà l’ó máa di aládùáà rẹgẹdẹ."
  42,34,"Tàbí kí Ó kó ìparun bá (àwọn ọkọ̀ ojú-omi náà) nítorí ohun tí àwọn èrò ọkọ̀ ojú-omi ṣe (níṣẹ́ aburú). Ó sì ń ṣàmójúkúrò níbi ọ̀pọ̀lọ́pọ̀."
  42,35,"Àwọn tó ń (fi irọ́) ja àwọn āyah Wa ní iyàn sì máa mọ̀ pé kò sí ibùsásí kan fún wọn."
  42,36,"Nítorí náà, ohunkóhun tí A bá fún yín, ìgbádùn ayé nìkan ni. Ohun tí ó wà lọ́dọ̀ Allāhu lóore jùlọ, ó sì máa ṣẹ́kù títí láéláé fún àwọn tó gbàgbọ́ ní òdodo, tí wọ́n sì ń gbáralé Olúwa wọn."
  43,16,"Tàbí (ẹ̀yin ń wí pé): “Ó mú nínú n̄ǹkan tí Ó dá ní ọmọbìnrin (fúnra Rẹ̀). Ó sì fi àwọn ọmọkùnrin ṣa ẹ̀yin lẹ́ṣà.”"
  43,17,"Nígbà tí wọ́n bá fún ẹnì kan nínú wọn ní ìró ìdùnnú ohun tí ó fi ṣe àpẹ̀ẹrẹ fún Àjọkẹ́-ayé, ojú rẹ̀ máa dúdú wá (pé òun bí ọmọbìnrin).{1} Ó sì máa kún fún ìbànújẹ́..",footnotes:1:[Òun kò fẹ́ bí ọmọbìnrin, ó sì lè pe àwọn mọlāika ní ọmọbìnrin Allāhu, Ọba tí kò bímọ!]
  43,18,"Ṣé ẹni tí wọ́n ń tọ́ nínú ọ̀ṣọ́ (tí ó ń to ọ̀ṣọ́ mọ́ra), tí kò sì lè bọ́ sí gban̄gba níbi ìjà (ni ẹ̀ ń pè ní ọmọ Àjọkẹ́-ayé)!?"
  44,1,"Hā mīm. (Allāhu ló mọ ohun tí Ó gbàlérò pẹ̀lú àwọn háràfí náà.){1}.",footnotes:1:[Ẹ wo ìtọsẹ̀-ọ̀rọ̀ sūrah al Baƙọrah; 2:1.]
  44,2,"(Allāhu) fi Tírà tó ń yanjú ọ̀rọ̀ ẹ̀dá búra."
  44,3,"Dájúdájú Àwa sọ̀ ọ́ kalẹ̀ nínú òru ìbùkún.{1} Dájúdájú Àwa ń jẹ́ Olùkìlọ̀..",footnotes:1:[Ẹ wo ìtọsẹ̀-ọ̀rọ̀ fún sūrah al-’Isrọ̄’; 17:106.]
